The Road Sector Project consists of the
            Government's 1986-1988 Road Investment and Maintenance
            Program. This program includes construction; reconstruction;
            upgrading; routine, periodic and deferred maintenance;
            consulting and training services and procurement of road
            maintenance equipment.

